57
00:03:30,769 --> 00:03:35,339
Both of these are pretty unattractive goals or unattractive outcomes.

58
00:03:35,339 --> 00:03:39,769
The reason why this is stressful is because no matter which one you choose, it’s likely

59
00:03:39,769 --> 00:03:42,459
that you won’t enjoy the experience at all.

60
00:03:42,459 --> 00:03:46,229
This is the most stressful type of conflict.

61
00:03:46,229 --> 00:03:51,859
Now there’s a third possibility, the approach-avoidance type, and this is NOT about a choice between

62
00:03:51,859 --> 00:03:53,620
