first time, and your id instantly opens its eyes and says, “This person is super hot.”

67
00:04:11,839 --> 00:04:15,709
So your id is really excited about this person, and it’s telling you, you should date this

68
00:04:15,709 --> 00:04:16,709
person.

69
00:04:16,709 --> 00:04:17,709
You’ve got to get to know them because you want to date them because they’re so hot.

70
00:04:17,709 --> 00:04:20,160
Now the problem is: even though they’re really hot, you noticed they’ve got some

71
