negative attributes.

72
00:04:21,279 --> 00:04:23,669
They really love Celine Dion!

73
00:04:23,669 --> 00:04:27,629
You have to decide whether to pursue a relationship with them.

74
00:04:27,629 --> 00:04:31,240
A relationship with this person means you get to spend lots of time with somebody who’s

75
00:04:31,240 --> 00:04:35,449
really hot, but also you’d be listening to Celine Dion.

76
00:04:35,449 --> 00:04:39,819
Or if you decide not to pursue your relationship with them, you don’t have to listen to Celine

77
00:04:39,819 --> 00:04:43,840
Dion, but you miss out on spending time with somebody you think is hot.

78
00:04:43,840 --> 00:04:48,460
You are to accept something positive and also something negative, or you’re choosing to

79
00:04:48,460 --> 00:04:52,360
avoid something negative but then lose something positive.

80
00:04:52,360 --> 00:04:57,639
The positive and negative aspects make it difficult to choose, and it can produce vacillation

81
00:04:57,639 --> 00:05:01,710
where we decide to pursue the goal and then decide not to pursue the goal at the same

82
